file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 0.1.0
  title: Test

components:
  schemas:
    Geometry:
      oneOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Line"
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Shape"
      discriminator:
        propertyName: type

    Line:
      type: object
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
        coordinates:
          type: array
          items:
            type: array
            items:
              type: number
              description: 3 dimensional point
              minItems: 3
              maxItems: 3
          minItems: 2
          maxItems: 2

    Shape:
      type: object
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
        coordinates:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/Line"
